id: pm-2cqx
title: MCP pm_list defaults to compact projection for agents
description: "pm_list MCP tool returned 79k chars for 4 in-progress items because projection defaulted to full (includes bodies, comments, all files). Now defaults to compact when no projection flag is set. Agents can opt out with options.compact=false or options.includeBody=true."
type: Issue
status: open
priority: 1
tags[5]: agent-ux,mcp,pm-cli,projection,token-efficiency
created_at: "2026-05-16T21:54:09.815Z"
updated_at: "2026-05-16T21:54:09.815Z"
author: maintainer-agent
acceptance_criteria: MCP pm_list default returns compact rows; description explains compact/brief/fields/limit options; opt-in to full output still available.
